{"id":239,"date":"2016-10-11T18:44:03","date_gmt":"2016-10-11T09:44:03","guid":{"rendered":"http:\/\/xsig.hpcc.jp\/?page_id=239"},"modified":"2016-10-11T18:44:03","modified_gmt":"2016-10-11T09:44:03","slug":"format","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/xsig.ipsj.or.jp\/2017\/en\/cfp\/format.html","title":{"rendered":"Paper Format"},"content":{"rendered":"<h3>Paper Format<\/h3>\n<dl>\n<dt>Language<\/dt>\n<dd>English or <a href=\"\/cfp\/format\/\">Japanese<\/a>.<\/dd>\n<dt>Necessary Items<\/dt>\n<dd>The format is not restricted as long as the following items are included\uff1a<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u201cxSIG 2017 Confidential Draft \u2014 Do NOT Distribute!\u201d at the top of the 1st page.<\/li>\n<li>Title<\/li>\n<li>Authors and Affiliations<\/li>\n<li>Abstract<\/li>\n<li>Main Matter<\/li>\n<li>References<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>Other items than these (e.g., acknowledgment) can be included (within word limits).<\/dd>\n<dt>Word Limits<\/dt>\n<dd><em>Less than<\/em> approximately 8,000 words. No limit for references.<\/dd>\n<dt>LaTeX<\/dt>\n<dd>If you are using LaTeX, the following example description will produce a paper that complies with the xSIG format. Please note that it usually requires some modifications, depending on your style file.<\/p>\n<blockquote><p><tt>begin{flushright}<br \/>\nfbox{large xSIG 2017 Confidential Draft -- Do NOT Distribute! }<br \/>\nend{flushright}<br \/>\nvspace*{2ex}<br \/>\nbegin{center}<br \/>\n{huge Title of your paper}<br \/>\nvspace*{3ex}<br \/>\n{large Name of Author 1 $^{*1}$hspace{1em}<br \/>\nName of Author 2 $^{*1}$hspace{1em}<br \/>\nName of Author 3 $^{*2}$hspace{1em}<br \/>\n...}<br \/>\nvspace*{2ex}<br \/>\n$^{*1}$Affiliation 1<br \/>\nvspace*{2ex}<br \/>\n$^{*2}$Affiliation 2<br \/>\nend{center}<br \/>\nsection*{Abstract}<br \/>\nWrite the abstract of your paper here.<\/tt><\/p><\/blockquote>\n<\/dd>\n<\/dl>\n<p>We will collect before the workshop the manuscripts for on-line distribution during the workshop.<\/p>\n<h3>Bachelor\/Master Thesis and Paper to Submit<\/h3>\n<p>We welcome papers that serves the base for bachelor\/master theses.<\/p>\n<p>However, a thesis and a papers to submit are different from the purpose. If you try to submit a paper that servers the base for your thesis, attention should be paid to the following items:<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>Do not write \u201cBachelor\/Master Thesis\u201d in the header.<\/li>\n<li>Include all the authors (including you).<\/li>\n<li>Do not write the adviser or the date of submission to the university office.<\/li>\n<li>Pay attention to the recipient and contents of the acknowledgement.<\/li>\n<\/ul>\n<p>&lt;!&#8211;<br \/>\n\u524d\u8a18\u306e\u6587\u5b57\u6570\u30fb\u30ef\u30fc\u30c9\u6570\u5236\u9650\u3092\u8d85\u904e\u3057\u306a\u3044\u5834\u5408\u3067\u3042\u3063\u3066\u3082\uff0c\u6280\u8853\u7684\u5185\u5bb9\u306b\u6bd4\u3057\u3066\u9577\u3059\u304e\u308b\u8ad6\u6587\u306f\u4e00\u822c\u306b\u6e1b\u70b9\u306e\u5bfe\u8c61\u306b\u306a\u308a\u307e\u3059\uff0e\u7279\u306b\uff0c\u5352\u696d\u8ad6\u6587\u30fb\u4fee\u58eb\u8ad6\u6587\u306e\u30d9\u30fc\u30b9\u3068\u306a\u308b\u8ad6\u6587\u3092\u6295\u7a3f\u3059\u308b\u5834\u5408\u306b\u306f\uff0c\u4ee5\u4e0b\u3092\u63a8\u5968\u3057\u307e\u3059\uff0c\u3059\u306a\u308f\u3061\uff1a<br \/>\n\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58\u3092\uff0c<\/p>\n<ul>\n<li>\u5f53\u8a72\u5206\u91ce\u306e\u5c02\u9580\u5bb6\u306a\u3089\u77e5\u3063\u3066\u3044\u308b\u3067\u3042\u308d\u3046\u4e00\u822c\u7684\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58 \u3068\uff0c\n<li>\u5f53\u8a72\u5206\u91ce\u306e\u5c02\u9580\u5bb6\u306b\u5bfe\u3057\u3066\u3067\u3082\u8aac\u660e\u3092\u8981\u3059\u308b\u3067\u3042\u308d\u3046\u8ad6\u6587\u56fa\u6709\u306e\u80cc\u666f\u77e5\u8b58<\/ul>\n<p style=\"text-indent: 0em\">\u306b\uff0c\u7ae0\u30fb\u7bc0\u3092\u5206\u3051\u3066\u8a18\u8ff0\u3057\u3066\u304a\u304d\uff0c\u6295\u7a3f\u8ad6\u6587\u3067\u306f\u524d\u8005\u3092\u7701\u7565\u3059\u308b\u306e\u3067\u3059\uff0e<\/p>\n<p>\u3053\u308c\u3089\u3092\u5206\u3051\u3066\u8a18